    {
      "id": "PopularPost96413",
      "post_content": "I like this card, becase it CAN make my deck win on turn 2, (without disruption)  \n  \nTurn 1: Lay Mountain and play [Goblin Guide](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Guide), then exile [Simian Spirit Guide](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Simian Spirit Guide) to enchant it with Taste for Mayhem, and Swing for 4.  \n  \nNow you should have 3 cards in hand.  \n  \nTurn 4: Lay mountain, use 2 mountains and another Spirit Guide to cast [Ball Lightning](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ball Lightning), and you should have 1 card in your hand (that you drew this turn). Now you can play your [Fireblast](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fireblast), saccing your 2 mountains and putting your opponent on 12, as well as making Goblin Guide a 6/2, now swing with both your 6 power creatures for the win!  \n  \nIt never happens, but 1 mana for 6 damage going somewhere isn't bad, I think this card should be rated higher. 4.0 for me.",
      "posted_by": "Kurraga",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost96413\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">I like this card, becase it CAN make my deck win on turn 2, (without disruption)<br/><br/>Turn 1: Lay Mountain and play <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Goblin Guide\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Guide\">Goblin Guide</a>, then exile <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Simian Spirit Guide\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Simian Spirit Guide\">Simian Spirit Guide</a> to enchant it with Taste for Mayhem, and Swing for 4.<br/><br/>Now you should have 3 cards in hand.<br/><br/>Turn 4: Lay mountain, use 2 mountains and another Spirit Guide to cast <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ball Lightning\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ball Lightning\">Ball Lightning</a>, and you should have 1 card in your hand (that you drew this turn). Now you can play your <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fireblast\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fireblast\">Fireblast</a>, saccing your 2 mountains and putting your opponent on 12, as well as making Goblin Guide a 6/2, now swing with both your 6 power creatures for the win!<br/><br/>It never happens, but 1 mana for 6 damage going somewhere isn't bad, I think this card should be rated higher. 4.0 for me.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '96413'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            