    {
      "id": "PopularPost324142",
      "post_content": "In-block, this owned Limited with the likes of [Flaring Flame-Kin](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flaring Flame-Kin). A decent, cheap enchantment that can potentially net you 4 or more damage for a single ![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol). While nowhere near as good as something like [Rancor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rancor) in constructed, nevertheless this is quite a decent power booster.",
